description:
Service Usage

The service notifies eMedical of changes in the back-end system (HAP / GCMS / IHS) regarding bio or contact details for previously cached Health Clients. It also modifies the relevant Health Client details stored in eMedical.
readme:
Service Usage

The service notifies eMedical of changes in the back-end system (HAP / GCMS / IHS) regarding bio or contact details for previously cached Health Clients. It also modifies the relevant Health Client details stored in eMedical.

Initiated upon the following business triggers:
Where client contact information has been updated
Where client bio-data has been updated

Service Behaviour

The back-end system (HAP / GCMS / IHS) will notify eMedical of changes in bio or contact details for previously cached Health Clients.
Asynchronous service.
